# NOTE: dist/ IS committed.
#
# Reason: this repo is consumed via `npm install github:owner/repo`.
# When npm clones a git dep on Windows, the `prepare` lifecycle does
# not reliably resolve `node_modules/.bin/tsc` on PATH (npm/cli #6119
# and friends). Committing pre-built dist/ removes the build step
# entirely and makes github-install a pure copy. Once we publish to
# npm proper, dist/ can move to .npmignore and out of git.
